title: Colin Jost | Manchin and Sinema Derail Biden's Agenda as Fox Fearmongers About It: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at two centrist Democrats blocking the entire Democratic agenda without saying what they want.

Then, Colin Jost talks about seeing Peyronie's disease commercials, his mom’s reaction to his son’s name and his friendship with Michael Che.
